{"tid":1467411,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我有個方法唔洗再捉鬼！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:49.000Z","uid":27578,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8990f3f3bbdae92885c24ff7fa1e4016ed9614a7","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗唔到呀！好高招"},{"pid":"2f6cf54461909c801031895a99e6016db1df38dd","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"317c5790ba5031302ef56c158bd9dfc8a97208dc","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d93716cc148bcc7a1530b42879bb5571ae0ec13d","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb75414944722ade19ca7a86c6d55520d6c14856","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"282458aa075d50c3e014694e124400ead160ed1d","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e58daa4a295b659b1b7874de7194b58afa4775cc","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eefdb680d8170f5774646838d46fffeef5f9d51","tid":1467411,"uid":261743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n要捉鬼，又要好睇<br />\n影出黎正面而有說服力<br />\n最好嘅方法，係叫記者去捉<br />\n<br />\n例如第一次喺cwb，tvb記者追問個垃圾係唔係狗，成件事已經令警察單位無任何說服力<br />\n<br />\n我地手足圍鬼，就一定有&quot;人&quot; 會打鬼<br />\n只要唔比佢走，叫記者過黎<br />\n1.說話盤問技巧比我地好<br />\n2.大大個cam影住佢點答都係死<br />\n3.夠正面，夠公道<br />\n4.只要比所有人知入面係有鬼，自然就無人再信警察單位<br />\n<br />\n簡單講之後做乜都可以，因為根本就係警察滲透到各層面而令暴力不斷出現。<br />\n佢呢一步好毒，但因爲太毒，同時風險都太高<br />\n因而有太多野比我地去反利用，要珍惜<br />\n<br />\nMedia時代，用media去解決問題<br />\n用media去令對方不斷失敗<br />\n任何外力，都可以係助力"},{"pid":"431df980264983de0e86ceb34b7314e4a9fd643d","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"冇人理？"},{"pid":"c8e6a02942df01e02cc98093a0f44d34fda6acb2","tid":1467411,"uid":84949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Royal-Hong-Kong-Regiment-The-Volunteers-712822242120609/?hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRoyal-Hong-Kong-Regiment-The-Volunteers-712822242120609%2F%3Fhc_location%3Dufi&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=6847d4ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Royal-Hong-Kong-Regiment-The-Volunteers-712822242120609/?hc_location=ufi</a><br />\n兩軍交戰有基本守則，如果偽裝成對方人員，被捕後可即場槍決 !<br />\n<br />\n1944年12月16日，盟軍登陸諾曼第後向德國逐步進逼，希特拉將所有兵力集中在比利時亞登地區，孤注一擲發動絕地反擊，展開突出部之役(Battle of Bulge)，並且派出由奧托.史科尼兹率領的一支受過特別訓練，並且能講流利美式英語的約160人特種部隊，穿上由戰俘身上獲得的美軍制服，裝備，武器及車輛，假扮成美軍，進行麒麟作戰(Operation Greif)。<br />\n<br />\n德軍特種部隊滲透到美軍後方，更改路標，制做混亂，誤導及趁機殺害毫無防範之小單位美軍。又佔據繆斯河上之橋樑，以保障德軍進攻通道暢通無阻，其後德軍反攻被盟軍瓦解，部隊遭到重創，損失約10萬兵員。<br />\n<br />\n而被捕德軍特種部隊成員由於身穿美軍軍服，故不受日內瓦國際公約(Geneva Conventions)保護，兼且觸犯戰爭罪行，被美軍指揮官命令憲兵即場執行槍決。"},{"pid":"a35c351823fd4ca2dbeb0af49367b3e620c70b06","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:57.000Z","msg":"都有道理"},{"pid":"bc4c5734be3707d21bb8b86f3ad8cc27e44d1222","tid":1467411,"uid":119467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0ab799a6bb80045d27949a867a07d534d409c05","tid":1467411,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"8d91a638063506a6c41c34966947be9f6a1d7163","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"又可以用打又可以盤問"},{"pid":"738f0cf6221f60c59c8ec77e0b2db34c69210480","tid":1467411,"uid":188432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"檢討文<br />\n<br />\n(集思廣益長文) 求大家用2分鐘時間睇睇 解決問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee36d68bd572121187d80007346ae9d5654e0abe","tid":1467411,"uid":157037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n612。721。811"},{"pid":"1da548189b6ac0144719835bf295c3451e807e4d","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:01.000Z","msg":"大家互相配合就得"},{"pid":"068bb983de5b272b667b0298c863cfdc8934297f","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"文宣唔洗講太多道理"},{"pid":"8fa2941058c1fadf4904b3a52f5e8e609f24fb75","tid":1467411,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大底線<br />\n1. 不打記者 <br />\n2. 不打救護<br />\n3. 不濫用酷刑 <br />\n4. 不攻擊平民<br />\n5.  冷靜，不被帶風向，要獨立思考</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1e2216c2fde55ab6725b1a994df631c946078f6d","tid":1467411,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:49.000Z","msg":"記住所有手足共識：<br />\n1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏"},{"pid":"1eea159eb78344cde534445daec3ad40662cb8c8","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"要既係激起民憤"},{"pid":"2af7684b4a58134d4110b2c816e18cdd11c116d5","tid":1467411,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"關於分化 我有少少嘢想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466107</a>"},{"pid":"7c24b5345d7b9c50ddd6f29fd5a911ba58fe20fa","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"推有用post"},{"pid":"e1c64592e97b866c378962d36b24373f22b191c2","tid":1467411,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"唔好比811火遮眼，<br />\n雖然比著係我知道係環時呢條遺害13億人既文化毒瘤，我都會忍唔到手。"},{"pid":"6e35f44436f3e67f3a1681d1c2f11b32b3952919","tid":1467411,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"啲咩輸緊既post都on99"}]}